{"tid":2033242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共有 6 人因示威活動送院，其中 1 名女士情況危殆","createTime":"2020-05-24T14:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T00:44:29.000Z","uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c92cee5e79ce2763b99c3a17d2401b701a489d1c","tid":2033242,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"北京主動出手制定「港版國安法」引起極大爭議，有網民發起今日（24日）在灣仔、銅鑼灣一帶遊行抗議。遊行開始不久，大批市民已佔據馬路，隨即爆發警民衝突，警方施放多枚催淚彈並發射水炮。警方表示，截至下午 4 時半，至少 120 人被捕，大部分均涉嫌非法集結。醫管局指，截至下午六時，共有 6 人因示威活動送院，其中 1 名女士情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a22d25c8acf8eb333bd105630549b3782586a76","tid":2033242,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"尼泊爾清潔工來，話廁所突然間一大堆人入嚟，嚇到心臟病發危殆"},{"pid":"caf7fa01afdd1a2526e5533629b8f6b47e4478da","tid":2033242,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a22d25c8acf8eb333bd105630549b3782586a76","tid":2033242,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"尼泊爾清潔工來，話廁所突然間一大堆人入嚟，嚇到心臟病發危殆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1a1432b6a52b33567fe50cc6028179d9